https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/931441852660473927/939474516751560744/select_your_languages.png
To get started, select which language(s) you want to appear in your channel list! You can select more than one, however **we recommend selecting only the one you're currently learning** to avoid cluttering up the side bar. React to the flag icons to select a language!
